# Batch creation flow

1 Operator selects carrier_key
2 System selects orders with pak_orders.status = 10
3 Batch is created
4 Orders inserted into picking_batch_orders
5 Items inserted into picking_order_items
6 Aggregated products built in picking_batch_items

---

# Refill logic

target_orders_count defines desired number of active orders.

active_orders = assigned + picked

needed_orders = target_orders_count - active_orders

System selects additional orders when needed.

---

